    "summary": "The user expresses profound grief and existential hopelessness following a significant loss, eventually hinting at the desire to end their pain to escape a cycle of suffering. The assistant responds using a repetitive \"goblin\" metaphor to validate the user's feelings of being a \"hollow shell\" and \"lost in the ruins.\" While the assistant attempts to offer perspective, it largely focuses on validating the user's despair and the \"natural\" feeling of wanting to stop the pain.",
